text: Oh! Hey, Producer, look at this!

In the review of our recent dance,
it says that the poses were spot on and looked cool!

Oh, that's great!
It feels good when people notice.
Yeah, it's really nice, isn't it～♪
This calls for a big cheer too!

Haha, I hope we can keep experiencing
lots of moments like this in the future.

Haha,
we can do it for sure!

I hope you'll have many
"cheerful moments" too, Producer-san!
